      <Value><![CDATA[<p>What is a PAT System?</p>
<div class="page">
<div class="section">
<div class="layoutArea">
<div class="column">
<p>The PAT system’s main purpose is to provide support to all students so that they can:</p>
<p>Optimise learning opportunities in every year of their programme</p>
<p>get the best advise about dealing with academic and personal issues.</p>
